{"tid":1771541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳帆：若鐵路不受破壞　運作及沙中綫進度不會受影響","createTime":"2019-12-06T03:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T12:43:30.000Z","uid":240448,"like":4,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f0db546cda4ab9788935f395afa4e674b548f05f","tid":1771541,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"立法會交鐵路事宜小組委員會討論沙中綫工程進展，港鐵表示，<em>[size=5<span style=\"color: violet;\">]截至9月30日，工程已完成91%</span>[/size=5]</em>。東鐵綫包括大學站近期受到破壞，要進行修復工作，估計「紅磡至金鐘段」要到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2022</span></strong></span>年才可開通。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨楊岳橋關注，政府及港鐵的說法是否認為若沒有反修例運動，沙中綫的工程就不會被延誤。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆說，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">若鐵路系統不受破壞，日常運作就不會受影響，項目進度亦不受影響</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-06 HKT 10:31"},{"pid":"96c8c64299bd0625efe78ed0fb273661865d1624","tid":1771541,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496261-20191206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496261-20191206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=2e1dee83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496261-20191206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ceea3e87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496261-20191206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6f87677fa168b3336940bf2c7654043fbf391aa4","tid":1771541,"uid":196924,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"明明係個紅磡站本身錯漏百出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16927127361c4ba926a40950a12ca607b58720f","tid":1771541,"uid":240448,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6f87677fa168b3336940bf2c7654043